com.bluegosling.concurrent.unsafe

Class UnsafeFieldUpdater<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bluegosling.concurrent.unsafe.UnsafeFieldUpdater<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type that owns the fields acted on
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnsafeIntegerFieldUpdater, UnsafeLongFieldUpdater, UnsafeReferenceFieldUpdater

    public abstract class UnsafeFieldUpdater<T>
extends Object
    A base class for classes that provide unsafe access to atomic operations on fields of another type. This is mostly a marker class in the hierarchy.
